CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 29, 1963, pg. 19, reads: "1963 Courier-WAMO Home-A-Rama Exhibitors who were not shown on last week's picture page are shown here... 14. Dulany Foods Inc. Elliott H. Barden and Larry J. Satariano... All Home-A-Rama Photos (Including last week's) by Charles (Teenie) Harris."
